sequenceDiagram
    participant P as PacMan
    participant G as Ghost (Frightened)
    participant EB as EventBus
    participant SM as ScoreManager
    participant GM as GameManager

    Note over P,G: Ghost in Frightened State

    P->>G: OnCollision(IEntity)
    G->>G: CheckState() - Is Frightened
    G->>EB: Publish(GhostEaten, ghostData)
    EB->>SM: Notify(GhostEaten)
    SM->>SM: AddPoints(200/400/800/1600)
    EB->>GM: Notify(GhostEaten)
    GM->>G: ReturnToGhostHouse()
    G->>G: SetState(Eaten)
    G->>G: Navigate to Ghost House
    G->>G: SetState(Scatter)
